{"type":"question","id":20408,"title":"如何平价东北广州商户抗议潮？","uid":34180,"topics":[5300,26,3755,5288,3159,988],"contents":"<b>时间：</b>似乎在本周3/5左右发生，具体时间不详。<br>\n<br>\n<b>地点1：东北</b><br>\n商户要求商场退还2月3月租金。诉求为“二三月退费，四五月减半”。<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TuCaoFakeNews/status/1235480842543067136\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TuCaoFakeNews/status/1235480842543067136</a><br>\n<br>\n<b>地点2：广东-广州和深圳（标题说“广州”，有误，但无法更正，特此注明。）</b><br>\n<br>\n广州十三行诚大时装广场商户在商场内流动抗议，口号“2月免租，3月减租”。<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Today__China/status/1235591429683965953\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Today__China/status/1235591429683965953</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E5%8F%AB%E5%8A%9B%E5%A5%B8\">叫力奸</a>指出，广州十三行诚大时装广场的抗议，已喷胡椒水：<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tucaofakenews/status/1235990026564988928\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tucaofakenews/status/1235990026564988928</a><br>\n<br>\n深圳商场外也有聚众抗议，大喊“抗议”<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Today__China/status/1235951914820354048\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Today__China/status/1235951914820354048</a><br>\n<br>\n警察已出动<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Today__China/status/1235945846258028544\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Today__China/status/1235945846258028544</a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n广东情况附截图：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/fuKvgWa.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fuKvgWa.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fuKvgWa.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/v4IsrbD.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/v4IsrbD.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/v4IsrbD.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RBcs6Pf.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RBcs6Pf.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RBcs6Pf.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-03-06","agreeCount":23,"discussionCount":23}